Project information.

Project information.

projects

Format

A data frame with 13 variables:

application.id

unique ID for the EXPORTER database

project.num

core project number, e.g. R01GM1234556

activity

activity code, e.g. R01

application.type

one-digit code to identify type of application funded

arra.funded

'Y' indicates ARRA funded, 'N' and 'NA' are not ARRA funded

suffix

'A'mended and 'S'upplmental + serial number

institute

administering institute

fiscal.year

year of funding

foa.number

parent FOA

project.start

in ymd format

project.end

in ymd format

study.section

3 letter code

fy.cost

total (direct + indirect) for fiscal year

Source

http://exporter.nih.gov/ExPORTER_Catalog.aspx?sid=3&index=0
